            "title": "Why Some People Are More Creative Than Others",
            "summary": "Scan over the cards and see what sentences have formed from the random arrangement of words. This is the eureka effect, our experience of suddenly comprehending something that was previously incomprehensible. The title of the cartoon is the \u201cThe Creative Moment\u201d and is a fabulous caricature of one of the most important discoveries in history."
